## Бэкапы

### Автоматические бэкапы (cron на сервере)

```bash
# /opt/memory-service/scripts/backup.sh
#!/bin/bash
set -e

BACKUP_DIR="/opt/memory-service/backups"
DATE=$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S)
RETENTION_DAYS=30

mkdir -p $BACKUP_DIR

# PostgreSQL
docker compose -f /opt/memory-service/docker-compose.yml \
  -f /opt/memory-service/docker-compose.prod.yml \
  exec -T postgres pg_dump -U memoryservice memoryservice \
  | gzip > $BACKUP_DIR/pg_$DATE.sql.gz

# MySQL (WordPress)
docker compose -f /opt/memory-service/docker-compose.yml \
  -f /opt/memory-service/docker-compose.prod.yml \
  exec -T mysql mysqldump -u wordpress -p$WP_DB_PASSWORD wordpress \
  | gzip > $BACKUP_DIR/wp_$DATE.sql.gz

# Удалить старые бэкапы
find $BACKUP_DIR -type f -mtime +$RETENTION_DAYS -delete

echo "Backup completed: $DATE"
```

```bash
# Cron: ежедневно в 4:00
sudo crontab -e
0 4 * * * /opt/memory-service/scripts/backup.sh >> /var/log/memory-service-backup.log 2>&1
```

### .gitignore дополнение

```gitignore
backups/
```

